{"tid":594020,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"太太cancer手術後4個月暴瘦廿磅是否正常？","createTime":"2018-03-15T13:05:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T16:14:03.000Z","uid":134683,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0a30a8abed2eb0698ee708db7d5bbe89f6340441","tid":594020,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:05:11.000Z","msg":"[url]老婆cancer今日做手術<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/483151/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/483151/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android[/url]<br />\n<br />\n首先再一次多謝大家支持同鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n太太11月尾砌乳癌腫瘤同4粒淋巴<br />\n化驗結果話個癌細胞有3.5cm<br />\n不過壞既只有不足0.5mm<br />\n醫生唔建議做化療<br />\n目前太太已完成電療<br />\n休息多半個月可以返工<br />\n但係做完手術至今瘦左成廿磅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能同佢食少左野同每日散步半小時有關<br />\n不過我好擔心之前d高放射性檢驗同手術trigger左佢其他cancer<br />\n佢依家當左自己好返哂<br />\n我有咩方法可以tum佢去check?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cc25d097e34d0da491c3d1aa4cc7fc16fb0881","tid":594020,"uid":76370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"巴打 最好飲番營養品補充番 太瘦真係唔得啊... 瘦會有好多complications 出黎"},{"pid":"3528632e5fb5297eb1c326f9a07955dd9b61ed43","tid":594020,"uid":76370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40cc25d097e34d0da491c3d1aa4cc7fc16fb0881","tid":594020,"uid":76370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:06:36.000Z","msg":"巴打 最好飲番營養品補充番 太瘦真係唔得啊... 瘦會有好多complications 出黎"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T13:07:02.000Z","msg":"電療都會暴瘦"},{"pid":"69411f4661929a52bb31529df52caa4aab925e2e","tid":594020,"uid":134683,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15